{"tid":1119311,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"【突發】有無人喺今日5:19聽到幾下怪聲","createTime":"2019-04-21T22:08:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-21T23:03:36.000Z","uid":6231,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"080ce7d7eb55f2062d12cf5c15200aa2284dc602","tid":1119311,"uid":6231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T22:08:27.000Z","msg":"話說我本身瞓緊覺，突然聽到一下好似震機咁嘅聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我第一反應掂下我隻貓，佢都即刻醒咗行去床尾，咁好自然我就坐起身去床尾搵電話。<br />\n<br />\n點知我掂到個電話嗰一刻，個怪聲停咗一停就即刻再響，而我個電話都唔係震緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n正當我諗緊個聲喺邊嘅時候，突然喺廁所嘅抽濕機又因為滿咗水而響。而個抽濕機響完嘅同時個怪聲就消失咗⋯⋯ <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個聲仲係好近好似喺窗邊，似震機又似船泊岸又似有人「hmmmmm」咁樣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請問有無人啱啱都聽到或者聽過一樣嘅聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3cf7286503e9a950799a8744a9803c3d910df7e","tid":1119311,"uid":14866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T22:10:04.000Z","msg":"清下世小心d"},{"pid":"6b0449fa8cdfa6f8b95f86a217cdf9cac1669f9c","tid":1119311,"uid":208180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T22:11:46.000Z","msg":"有雀"},{"pid":"900f6614be0f58b87e1056fb4b2c23da4fff8939","tid":1119311,"uid":186543,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T22:44:13.000Z","msg":"24567111幫到你"},{"pid":"b421be9dca0d2ff8613eb2fea6a790c5d0a93884","tid":1119311,"uid":114484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T22:46:24.000Z","msg":"你個名"},{"pid":"7600da3fe2d1fb18eb497dd3f63ac1d78823915e","tid":1119311,"uid":183358,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T22:50:34.000Z","msg":"住九龍